{"tid":1081410,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"牛B死了，美斯本賽季各項賽事37場比賽直接參與60球","createTime":"2019-03-28T09:16:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T20:58:27.000Z","uid":134997,"like":34,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"a664d769a65d8fbd647e42b94770c075a8bc7f31","tid":1081410,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T09:16:55.000Z","msg":"據統計，在本賽季各項賽事出戰的37場比賽中，美斯總共製造了60球，其中他打進39球，送出了21次助攻。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然阿根廷隊在此前的熱身賽中負於委内瑞拉，但這並不能掩蓋美斯在本賽季的出色表現，他已經在各項賽事中直接參與了60球。<br />\n<br />\n如果唔計12碼，美斯參與的進球數有55個。若是僅僅關注西甲聯賽，美斯參與的進球數一共為43個。<br />\n<br />\n本賽季參與進球數排名：<br />\n<br />\n1 美斯 60球<br />\n<br />\n2 唔計12碼的美斯 55球<br />\n<br />\n3 西甲聯賽中的美斯 43球<br />\n<br />\n4 姆巴佩 42球<br />\n<br />\n5 唔計助攻的美斯 39球<br />\n<br />\n6 C朗拿度 36球<br />\n<br />\n7 史達寧 35球<br />\n<br />\n7 阿古路 35球<br />\n<br />\n9 賓施馬 30球<br />\n<br />\n10 尼馬 29球"},{"pid":"ae5c95265c01c2ebdef2614948f18e7d38e97cfe","tid":1081410,"uid":134997,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T09:17:35.000Z","msg":"助攻唔計12碼唔計"},{"pid":"93bcb00b4f155dde568d8aaa056d4fdcc683cf6c","tid":1081410,"uid":47717,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T09:25:40.000Z","msg":"呢啲post通常冇人回應"},{"pid":"66f9e304337570d22833ea46fa9313c356b74c43","tid":1081410,"uid":20209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T09:25:51.000Z","msg":"賓斯馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e74764b8220f4e021a3e02e6e130b29e879ccded","tid":1081410,"uid":24750,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T09:36:14.000Z","msg":"和牛定松板牛"},{"pid":"2cc1efb74e4e790ad7c5962574571b7c8fc736d9","tid":1081410,"uid":35293,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T09:54:14.000Z","msg":"唔過2 頁"},{"pid":"60863397152d50fb39dc7799d5a83aae7fd8d7a3","tid":1081410,"uid":119024,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,